WEBVTT

00:00:28.581 --> 00:00:37.471
HAYOM YOM REVII, HAESRIM VESHEVA BENOVEMBER, ELEF TSHA MEOT TISHIM VESHESH, TET ZAYIN KISLEV, TAV SHIN NUN ZAYIN.

00:00:37.471 --> 00:00:42.390
SHMI TOBY REISS-RUBIN VEANI OREKHET REAYON IM Lev Rozov

00:00:42.390 --> 00:00:44.673
BEIR NATANYA, YISRAEL.

00:00:48.561 --> 00:00:53.865
HAYOM YOM REVII, HAESRIM VESHEVA BENOVEMBER, ELEF TSHA MEOT TISHIM VESHESH,

00:00:53.865 --> 00:00:56.560
TET ZAYIN KISLEV, TAV SHIN NUN ZAYIN.

00:00:56.560 --> 00:01:00.935
SHMI TOBY REISS-RUBIN VEANI OREKHET REAYON IM Lev Rozov

00:01:00.935 --> 00:01:03.152
BEIR NATANYA, YISRAEL.

00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:07.650
UNK ⟨vet⟩ zayn in ordenung ales.

00:01:09.199 --> 00:01:15.800
SHALOM ADON Rozov. ⟨ikh v- h-⟩ ir kent mir zogn ayer nomen un GEBURTSDATUM, bite?

00:01:16.152 --> 00:01:18.120
 ⟨ersh-⟩...

00:01:18.143 --> 00:01:20.128
dos iz a dertseylung

00:01:20.252 --> 00:01:22.169
fun a mishpokhe,

00:01:22.193 --> 00:01:24.640
fun a yidisher mishpokhe,

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:30.152
vos zaynen nitsl gevorn fun dem HITLEROVSKn Natsishn merder.

00:01:30.917 --> 00:01:32.110
⟨ershtns⟩.

00:01:32.110 --> 00:01:35.383
ikh bin gebor- ikh bin Rozov Lev,

00:01:35.608 --> 00:01:37.677
geborn in Dokshits

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:43.620
in, in zibetn yor, toyznt nayn hundert zibn,

00:01:44.299 --> 00:01:46.318
 z-, zibete,

00:01:46.510 --> 00:01:49.570
zibetn ⟨A-⟩ zibetn IUL'.

00:01:49.497 --> 00:01:52.748
zibetn yuli, toyznt nayn hundert zibn?

00:01:51.070 --> 00:01:52.070
UNK

00:01:52.213 --> 00:01:53.051
zibn.

00:01:52.888 --> 00:01:55.745
vu, in v- ⟨in D-⟩ velkhe shtot? Dokshits?

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:58.550
shto- shtot Do-... ikh'l aykh z-... shtot Dokshits.

00:01:58.550 --> 00:02:01.736
shtot, shtot Dokshits, bay eltern,

00:02:01.736 --> 00:02:05.830
mayn foter ruft men Yidl, Yidl,

00:02:05.848 --> 00:02:08.850
un er iz geborn gevorn

00:02:08.850 --> 00:02:12.659
in toyznt akht hundert zibetsik nayn,

00:02:12.767 --> 00:02:17.280
iz er geborn. di muter heyst SARA, UNK, SARA,

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:20.658
un zi iz geborn gevorn in Rusland

00:02:20.749 --> 00:02:26.710
in toyznt, in toyznt akht hundert akhtsik fir.

00:02:27.803 --> 00:02:30.311
gelebt hobn mir in Dokshits,

00:02:30.418 --> 00:02:32.620
gelebt hobn mir in Dokshits,

00:02:32.620 --> 00:02:37.246
in a eygene ⟨hoyz do-⟩ in a eygene hoyz, mit a ⟨b-⟩ shtikl erd.

00:02:37.270 --> 00:02:39.660
bay undz hot zikh gefirt a balebatishkeyt.

00:02:39.987 --> 00:02:42.698
di gantsene farnem fun di

00:02:42.838 --> 00:02:45.937
balebatishkeyt, dos hot gehert tsu der muter.

00:02:46.045 --> 00:02:48.857
der foter iz geven a religyezer mentsh.

00:02:49.082 --> 00:02:51.382
er iz gegangen in kloyz,

00:02:51.382 --> 00:02:54.140
un er volt shtendik lernen, nor er hot zikh farnumen,

00:02:54.140 --> 00:02:59.134
er hot zikh farnumen oykh, gor a mol iz er geven a melamed, gor a mol,

00:02:59.308 --> 00:03:02.862
un nakher iz er ibergegangen, gemakht an aynbinderay,

00:03:03.122 --> 00:03:06.450
un volt zikh farnemen a bisl mit handl. ⟨o- d-...⟩

00:03:05.321 --> 00:03:07.970
an aynbinderay, a bukh-binderay?

00:03:06.987 --> 00:03:08.600
a bukh-binderay.

00:03:07.970 --> 00:03:09.208
yo.

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:10.390
dos iz a bukh-binderay.

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:15.336
nu, un er hot zikh, az s'iz nit geven vos tsu ton, volt ⟨zikh⟩ farnemen mit a bisl handl.

00:03:15.336 --> 00:03:17.544
s'iz geven a kleyn shtetl.

00:03:17.584 --> 00:03:22.083
 ikh vil nokh fregn iber di muter. vi hot di muter geheysn fun shtub?

00:03:21.803 --> 00:03:23.909
⟨un⟩ fun shtub hot zi geheysn

00:03:23.909 --> 00:03:25.864
SARA Fridman.

00:03:25.580 --> 00:03:28.650
Fridman. un di mame hot oykh gearbet?

00:03:26.382 --> 00:03:27.382
⟨F⟩⟨UNK⟩...

00:03:27.827 --> 00:03:31.710
di mame, di mame hot gefirt di balebatishkeyt.

00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:38.470
zi hot UNK gefirt di gantse balebatishkeyt, mit hodeven kinder, iz dos geven di mame's arbet.

00:03:38.526 --> 00:03:41.304
zi hot nit gearbet vayle s'iz bay undz geven

00:03:41.496 --> 00:03:43.785
UNK a sakh kinder.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:46.198
vifl briders un shvesters hot ir gehat?

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:50.951
mir hobn... ikh'l aykh dertseyln glaykh. fir brider hobn mir gehat un dray shvester,

00:03:50.951 --> 00:03:52.610
vos ikh gedenk.

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:55.220
ikh zog vos ikh gedenk.

00:03:56.093 --> 00:03:59.428
eyn bruder, eyn bruder iz bay undz geshtorbn

00:03:59.586 --> 00:04:05.554
fun a harts-krankeyt, vos in yene tsayt hot men nit gekont dos heyln.

00:04:06.150 --> 00:04:09.029
iz er geshtorbn alt tsvelf yor.

00:04:09.778 --> 00:04:13.434
tsvelf ⟨yor⟩. zaynen mir geblibn dray brider

00:04:13.457 --> 00:04:15.003
mit dray shvester.

00:04:15.425 --> 00:04:17.010
ir zent geven...

00:04:16.005 --> 00:04:18.727
ikh bin geven der elterer.

00:04:18.727 --> 00:04:21.849
nokh mir iz geven a eltere shvester,

00:04:21.849 --> 00:04:24.127
un s'iz geven a bruder

00:04:24.127 --> 00:04:26.886
nokh di shvester. nakher iz geven

00:04:26.886 --> 00:04:31.287
vayter a shvester un vayter a bru- un vayter a shvester.

00:04:29.370 --> 00:04:34.747
vi hobn zey geheysn? ir kent mir zogn di nomen fun di briders un shvesters?

00:04:33.066 --> 00:04:35.090
a, ikh kon zogn.

00:04:35.732 --> 00:04:39.118
d- di eltere shvester hot geheysn DVORA,

00:04:40.609 --> 00:04:46.440
un di, DVORA, un di ander shvester hot geheysn ASYA.

00:04:46.785 --> 00:04:49.850
der bruder hot geheysn Shmuel-Ber,

00:04:51.072 --> 00:04:56.090
tsvey nomen, un der ander bruder heyst Gedalye.

00:04:56.320 --> 00:05:02.500
oto dos iz, der Gedalye, ikh bin der eltster, un er iz der klenster.

00:05:03.711 --> 00:05:06.290
dos iz di mishpokhe undzere.

00:05:06.939 --> 00:05:13.140
vu iz geven dos shtot Duksh- Dokshits? nebn velkhe shtot, nebn velkhe groyse shtot?

00:05:11.558 --> 00:05:15.990
ot, itst, Dokshits... ikh'l ay-... Dokshits iz geven a shtot

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:21.795
azoy: vos zi hot zikh ongehoybn vu di taykh BEREZINA heybt zikh on.

00:05:21.852 --> 00:05:27.380
un zi hot gehert azoy: eyn shtot iz geven fun ir draysik kilometer, GLUBOKOE,

00:05:27.380 --> 00:05:31.906
geven oykh a shtot aza, nor a gresere fun Dokshits.

00:05:31.906 --> 00:05:37.471
gehert hobn mir tsu, ts- tsu dem voyevudst- tsu dem oblast fun Disne

00:05:37.883 --> 00:05:40.408
un di voyevudstve Vilne.

00:05:40.785 --> 00:05:44.520
fun Vilne zaynen mir geven tsvey hundert kilometer.

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:48.536
di ban-stantsye bay undz hot geheysn PARAF'YANOVO,

00:05:48.536 --> 00:05:54.490
vos mir hobn zikh mit ir di gantse tsayt genitst; zi hot geven shayekh tsu Dokshits.

00:05:54.268 --> 00:05:57.070
vi vayt iz es geven, di ban?

00:05:55.855 --> 00:05:57.671
tsen kilometer.

00:05:57.370 --> 00:06:03.172
iz tsen kilometer iz geven biz di ban, un tsvey hundert kilometer biz Vilne?

00:05:59.382 --> 00:06:00.793
biz der ban.

00:06:00.799 --> 00:06:03.290
un tsvey hundert kilometer biz Vilne.

00:06:04.022 --> 00:06:06.320
vi groys iz geven di shtot?

00:06:05.676 --> 00:06:10.450
di shtot, di shtot hot gehat a bafelkerung, umgefer

00:06:10.450 --> 00:06:14.220
fir toyznt, in algemeyn fir toyznt.

00:06:14.190 --> 00:06:15.930
un vi- vifl yidn?

00:06:14.653 --> 00:06:21.616
un di yidn zaynen geven a- ammerstn teyl, a, mer vi a helft zaynen geven dortn yidn.

00:06:20.745 --> 00:06:23.489
mer vi di helft zenen geven yidn?

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:23.526
zaynen geven yidn.

00:06:23.526 --> 00:06:27.510
di, vo-... o. vos hobn zikh farnumen di yidn, un vos...?

00:06:23.530 --> 00:06:24.780
ikh v-...

00:06:27.510 --> 00:06:33.432
di yidn hobn zikh farnumen ammerstn mit kleyn hantverkeray. ir veyst vos s'iz hantverkeray?

00:06:33.432 --> 00:06:35.640
mit f- balmelokhes:

00:06:36.085 --> 00:06:41.006
shuster, shnayder, stolyer, ⟨oto, oto⟩ di, di arbet.

00:06:41.147 --> 00:06:47.910
di poye-, di nit-yidn... poyer⟨UNK⟩... nit-yidn hobn zikh farnumen mit erd-arbet⟨er⟩,

00:06:47.910 --> 00:06:52.400
zaynen ale geven erd-, erd-arbeter zaynen zey geven, vayl zey hobn gehat

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:54.523
eygene, eygene bodn...

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:56.420
un di yidn hobn nisht gehat keyn eygene bodn?

00:06:55.272 --> 00:07:00.289
yidn, yidn ⟨iz,⟩ zaynen geven a tsvey, dray vos hobn gehat bodn,

00:07:00.289 --> 00:07:06.000
nor zey hobn nit gearbet oyf di bodn. yidn hobn zikh farnumen, geven azoy, balego-...

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.715
ikh'l aykh zogn azoy poshet: balegoles,

00:07:08.974 --> 00:07:12.750
di⟨,⟩ di, vos firn di,

00:07:12.750 --> 00:07:15.140
UNK vayle ale skhoyres

00:07:15.140 --> 00:07:19.987
vos in di gesheftn hot men gedarft, hobn mir alts gedarft, zol⟨n⟩ brengen fun Vilne.

00:07:19.673 --> 00:07:23.050
fun Vilne hot men gebrengt ales in gesheft?

00:07:20.787 --> 00:07:21.675
UNK

00:07:21.883 --> 00:07:24.390
alts in di, in di gesheftn,

00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:28.360
alts in di gesheftn. bay undz iz geven a fabrikl bir,

00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:31.634
a bir-fabrikl iz geven, bir-b⟨ureray⟩,

00:07:31.634 --> 00:07:37.959
un s'iz geven GAZ- GAZOZ, oto di ale iz geven, aza ⟨min sort f-⟩ fabrikl iz geven.

00:07:38.083 --> 00:07:40.493
un bay undz iz geven ammerstns

00:07:40.493 --> 00:07:42.262
hendler fun holts.

00:07:42.505 --> 00:07:44.410
geven a sakh velder,

00:07:44.410 --> 00:07:49.690
vos zey hobn afile holts geshikt oyf oysland oykh. nor holts-handl, dos iz geven,

00:07:49.690 --> 00:07:54.170
di handl iz geven hundert protsent in yidishe hent.

00:07:53.845 --> 00:08:00.390
, ir hot gehert tsu vel- tsu v- tsu, ⟨D-⟩ Dokshits hot gehert tsu Poyln, oder tsu Rusland?

00:07:54.503 --> 00:07:55.425
UNK

00:07:59.278 --> 00:08:03.160
o! Dokshits, Dokshits iz geven azoy: ⟨d-⟩

00:08:03.227 --> 00:08:06.191
far der ershter velt-krig,

00:08:06.265 --> 00:08:08.115
vos ikh gedenk,

00:08:08.172 --> 00:08:11.980
iz geven Dokshits gehert tsu Rusland.

00:08:11.980 --> 00:08:15.590
s'iz geven Barisever gubernye oyf rusish,

00:08:15.590 --> 00:08:20.380
un Minsker voy- un Minsker obla- un Minsker tsenter.

00:08:20.380 --> 00:08:23.450
Minsk iz geven di hoypt-shtot fun Vaysrusland,

00:08:23.450 --> 00:08:25.946
un Barisev iz geven undzer uyezdne shtot.

00:08:25.946 --> 00:08:29.650
Barisev iz fun undz oykh geven hundert zekhtsik kilometer,

00:08:29.650 --> 00:08:33.106
azoy UNK. bay undz iz azoy,

00:08:33.703 --> 00:08:39.290
a shtetl, a freylekhe shtetl, mit a sakh velder arum undz, ⟨a⟩...

00:08:38.462 --> 00:08:42.720
ober ir zogt, ir zent geven... SLIKHA az ikh, ikh vil nokh endikn...

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:47.190
ir zogt, ir zent, bizn ershtn velt-krig zent ir geven gehert tsu Rusland.

00:08:46.461 --> 00:08:47.653
tsu Rusland.

00:08:47.190 --> 00:08:48.590
un shpeter?

00:08:47.980 --> 00:08:51.875
un... o! shpe- a, dos ⟨hob ikh nit...⟩ shpeter, shpeter,

00:08:51.875 --> 00:08:58.310
in n- der, in der tsveyter velt-milkhome, ven s'iz gevorn di revolutsye in dem zibetsntn,

00:08:58.310 --> 00:08:59.960
in zibetsntn yor,

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:01.140
iz gevorn di velt-...

00:08:59.978 --> 00:09:01.920
nayntsn zibetsn?

00:09:01.140 --> 00:09:02.600
nayntsn zibetsn.

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:07.150
iz gevorn di revolutsye, hot Poyln zikh gemakht zelbshtendikeyt

00:09:07.150 --> 00:09:10.560
un zi hot mit di Sovyetn milkhome gehaltn,

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:15.525
iz hot zi farnumen Dokshits in tsvey un tsvantsiktn yor.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.390
⟨iz in⟩...

00:09:15.525 --> 00:09:17.890
iz nokh geven milkhome a bisl,

00:09:17.890 --> 00:09:22.196
nor nokhn, dortn, nokh dem MIR vos me hot gemakht dan,

00:09:22.270 --> 00:09:25.549
in di, fun di Sovyetn, dos vos, ikh veys nit,

00:09:25.549 --> 00:09:28.050
oder dos iz gevorn Poyln.

00:09:27.940 --> 00:09:32.558
iz nayntsn tsvey un tsvontsik iz gevorn Dokshits Poyln.

00:09:28.050 --> 00:09:32.590
Poyln iz gevo-... nayntsn tsvey un tsvantsik iz gevorn Poyln.

00:09:32.590 --> 00:09:37.361
iz di gantsene, alts iz ibergegangen oyf di poylishe kultur...

00:09:37.361 --> 00:09:41.290
⟨dos darf ikh oykh zogn...⟩ di poylishe kultur. iz shoyn gevorn

00:09:41.290 --> 00:09:43.930
poylishe shuln, a Tarbut shul

00:09:43.930 --> 00:09:47.376
iz geven bay undz, a yidishe shul iz geven bay undz,

00:09:47.376 --> 00:09:53.654
un s'iz geven UNK ⟨un,⟩ un hekher lernen zikh, hekher lernen zikh hobn mir gedarft

00:09:53.654 --> 00:10:01.690
onkumen i- oder in Vilne... in Vilne ammerstns. s'iz geven Glubok, volt zayn dortn a gimnazye nokh gevezn,

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:05.590
nor, nor forn lernen zikh hot men gedarft ale fakhn

00:10:05.790 --> 00:10:10.697
in Vilne. Vilne iz geven a shtot mit a, a tekhnikum,

00:10:10.697 --> 00:10:14.580
s'iz geven a te- a Hilf Durkh Arbet, Ort,

00:10:14.580 --> 00:10:17.470
ot azetike ale shuln. geven,

00:10:17.470 --> 00:10:21.610
di pedagogishe shuln iz gevezn in Vilne, a, a ivrit

00:10:21.610 --> 00:10:24.120
l- far lerer, un oyf yidish far lerer.

00:10:24.120 --> 00:10:26.910
dos iz alts in Vilne. ⟨me volt forn in Vilne⟩.

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:31.210
iz ven ir zent geven a kind, hot ir, ersht hot ir gelernt in di yidishe shul?

00:10:26.910 --> 00:10:29.224
ikh bin, ikh bin gev-...

00:10:29.770 --> 00:10:35.968
ikh bin geven a kind biz⟨n⟩ dem kumendik fun P- fun di ⟨p⟩oyln tsu undz,

00:10:35.968 --> 00:10:38.560
bin ikh gelernt in shtot,

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:42.630
do in di sh- do in⟨em⟩, in talmed-toyre, do,

00:10:42.630 --> 00:10:45.052
bay di rusn bin ikh gegangen in shule.

00:10:45.109 --> 00:10:50.920
UNK biz⟨n⟩ ikh hob bavizn bay di rusn tsu endikn di shule, zaynen shoyn geven di milkhome,

00:10:50.920 --> 00:10:53.101
mit di koyln. ikh bin nokh geven a kind.

00:10:53.277 --> 00:10:58.097
iz keyn, iz keyn, keyn hekher shul ⟨aleyn⟩ hob ikh shoyn nit durkhgemakht.

00:10:58.423 --> 00:11:02.602
bin ikh zikh avekgeforn lernen az mir iz shoyn alt geven zibetsn yor.

00:11:02.344 --> 00:11:03.610
keyn Vilne.

00:11:03.047 --> 00:11:05.110
keyn Vilne. in Vilne

00:11:04.275 --> 00:11:05.275
⟨un...⟩

00:11:05.110 --> 00:11:07.830
hob ikh zikh ongel- ongehoybn lernen,

00:11:07.830 --> 00:11:10.860
ongehoybn lernen in Hilf Durkh Arbet.

00:11:10.860 --> 00:11:13.290
dos iz geven... darf ikh oyfklern vos...

00:11:13.290 --> 00:11:17.435
dos iz geven a shul ⟨D-⟩ oysgehaltn fun Dzhoynt.

00:11:17.796 --> 00:11:20.260
di Amerikaner gezelshaft

00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:22.690
hot undz gemakht yidishe shuln.

00:11:22.690 --> 00:11:25.360
dortn iz geven KHUDOZHESTVENNe shuln,

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:28.930
s'iz geven far froyen shuln, a stoleray iz dortn gevezn,

00:11:28.930 --> 00:11:30.340
alts in der shul.

00:11:30.340 --> 00:11:33.242
ikh hob zikh gelernt dekorativ maleray.

00:11:33.242 --> 00:11:34.790
getrakht hob ikh a mol

00:11:34.790 --> 00:11:38.870
arbetn in teater... ir veyst dokh, in di yung- in di yunge yorn

00:11:38.870 --> 00:11:41.887
iz dokh andere, an ander g- andere gedanken.

00:11:42.062 --> 00:11:47.990
iz hob ikh gelernt zikh dortn. gelernt hob ikh dortn tsvey yor, nit geendikt.

00:11:48.255 --> 00:11:53.460
far vos? s'iz geven a tsayt, m'hot mir gedarft hobn in shtub.

00:11:54.297 --> 00:11:58.340
UNK der foter hot fardint veynik,

00:11:58.347 --> 00:12:02.992
un ikh bin avekgegangen arbetn. UNK eyner iz geven bay undz a KHUDOZHNIK;

00:12:02.992 --> 00:12:07.115
gemakht shutfes, un mir hobn gearbet shtub-maleray.

00:12:07.223 --> 00:12:10.150
hob ikh shoyn fardint gelt.

00:12:10.150 --> 00:12:14.253
kh'hob opgearbet di etlekhe yor, un nakher hot men mir tsugenumen in militer,

00:12:14.496 --> 00:12:16.650
in militer in Poyln.

00:12:16.669 --> 00:12:18.270
in velkhes yor?

00:12:18.464 --> 00:12:19.464
vo-...?

00:12:18.715 --> 00:12:21.440
velkhes yor hot men aykh genum-...?

00:12:19.812 --> 00:12:24.413
in velkhn yor? in akht, in, in akht un tsvantsiktn yor.

00:12:23.946 --> 00:12:28.220
in nayntsn akht un tsvontsik hot men aykh genumen in poylishn militer.

00:12:25.144 --> 00:12:29.106
nayntsn akht un tsvantsik UNK in poylishe militer genumen.

00:12:29.106 --> 00:12:32.840
poylishe militer hob ikh gedint tsvey yor,

00:12:32.840 --> 00:12:36.500
un draysiktn bin ikh gekumen krik aheym.

00:12:36.433 --> 00:12:39.180
tsurik aheym in nayntsn draysik.

00:12:37.210 --> 00:12:42.817
⟨a-⟩ draysik. in Poyln hob ikh gedint, ⟨ikh hob gedo-⟩ in Poyln hob ikh gedint azoy:

00:12:42.817 --> 00:12:46.970
gedint in Demblin. dos iz a poylishe shtot a krepost.

00:12:46.970 --> 00:12:50.390
nakher ⟨oder⟩ bin ikh geven a lontshnik

00:12:50.390 --> 00:12:55.479
in, in Varshe in, SZPITAL UJAZDOWSKI,

00:12:56.532 --> 00:12:59.920
hob ikh zikh farnumen mit telefonen, ⟨, ikh bin⟩ geven a lontshnik.

00:12:57.825 --> 00:12:59.730
UNK

00:12:59.923 --> 00:13:06.042
nu, dos iz geven, un fun dem, az m'hot mir bafrayt, bin ikh gekumen krik aheym.

00:13:06.133 --> 00:13:09.520
afile ikh hob gehat dortn a meydl, ikh hob gevolt...

00:13:09.520 --> 00:13:15.504
nor s'iz ge- nit geven... ikh'l aykh zogn, ikh hob gelitn ammerstn, mer fun ale. ikh bin geven der elterer.

00:13:15.504 --> 00:13:17.960
kh'hob gemuzt haltn di shtub.

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:22.921
di eltere, di eltere, der yingerer bruder iz gegangen nokh in Tarbut shul.

00:13:22.921 --> 00:13:27.407
di elt- di tokhter, eyne hot zikh gelernt in Vilne

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:30.670
un eyne hot zikh gelernt in Glubok bukhhalter,

00:13:30.670 --> 00:13:33.860
un m'hot yedern gedarft oyshaltn.

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:35.890
do bin ikh shoyn gevezn.

00:13:35.890 --> 00:13:39.473
ikh hob gezen az lere, dos iz di hoypt-zakh,

00:13:39.478 --> 00:13:44.124
un s'iz nit, bay di foter mit di muter iz dos nit geven azoy; zaynen geven

00:13:44.124 --> 00:13:47.288
amolike mentshn. er volt gemeynt, der foter,

00:13:47.288 --> 00:13:52.650
az me vet konen gut davnen oder lernen, dos iz geendikt oyf dem,

00:13:52.650 --> 00:13:57.000
nor ikh hob shoyn geven mer in shtot un in militer,

00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:59.870
in Varshe geven, un ikh hob alts shoyn gezen.

00:13:59.870 --> 00:14:02.828
hob ikh gezen az lere

00:14:02.901 --> 00:14:04.914
iz, di hoypt-zakh iz lere,

00:14:04.914 --> 00:14:08.810
iz lere, bin ikh gekumen aheym un ikh hob gearbet.

00:14:08.810 --> 00:14:12.614
kh'hob oyf, ikh hob gekrogn an arbet a gevise tsayt

00:14:13.330 --> 00:14:16.969
bay eynem a inzhenyer vos hot gearbet oyf di ayznban,

00:14:17.262 --> 00:14:22.790
oyf moln dortn mit di kolirn. hob ikh zey gedarft tsuzamenshteln kolirn. ikh hob, bin shoyn geven

00:14:22.790 --> 00:14:26.132
a bisl, nit geendikt, nor a bisl an arbeter.

00:14:26.138 --> 00:14:29.270
hob ikh gearbet dortn bay im a tsayt.

00:14:29.270 --> 00:14:33.970
a tsayt gearbet, un ikh hob gut fardint. ⟨ikh hob⟩ gehat a P.K.O. bikhl.

00:14:33.970 --> 00:14:37.360
ikh hob shoyn gehat a, a b- a banemung

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:39.075
in, in lebn,

00:14:39.233 --> 00:14:41.134
un ikh hob geholfn di shtub.

00:14:41.798 --> 00:14:45.470
der bruder... ikh hob nokh a bruder vos iz nito.

00:14:45.470 --> 00:14:49.200
er iz geven, er iz geven fun mir yinger oyf finf yor.

00:14:49.341 --> 00:14:52.400
nor er hot gehat a meydl,

00:14:52.648 --> 00:14:57.721
un er hot khasene gehat, avekgegangen fun shtub. ikh hob oykh gehat a libe.

00:14:57.778 --> 00:15:00.973
kh'hob gehat a meydl in der kleyner, in shtot.

00:15:00.973 --> 00:15:03.454
volt ikh oyf zumer kumen aheym,

00:15:03.454 --> 00:15:07.930
⟨hobn mir⟩ gehat aza... zi iz geven oykh oyf finf yor... az mir ir geven tsvantsik,

00:15:07.930 --> 00:15:09.646
iz ir geven fuftsn.

00:15:09.646 --> 00:15:13.499
ir farshteyt? UNK mit a fuftsn yorike meydl.

00:15:13.540 --> 00:15:16.419
di tsayt iz gegangen gikh.

00:15:16.510 --> 00:15:19.890
khasene hobn hobn mir nit gekont.

00:15:20.998 --> 00:15:24.030
⟨s'iz,⟩ ikh'l aykh zogn far vos:

00:15:24.222 --> 00:15:28.080
ikh bin nit geven, gekukt oyfn yidishn lebn

00:15:28.390 --> 00:15:31.095
in yene tsayt... nu, ikh bin shoyn geven in Varshe...

00:15:31.095 --> 00:15:34.930
oyfn yidishn lebn, yidisher lebn iz geven a oremer lebn.

00:15:35.376 --> 00:15:37.744
afile di kleynhendler,

00:15:37.744 --> 00:15:39.406
afile di kremer

00:15:39.406 --> 00:15:42.340
zaynen nit geven keyn groyse gvirim.

00:15:42.430 --> 00:15:46.840
Poyln, Poyln iz geven a oremkeyt.

00:15:46.840 --> 00:15:49.210
s'iz nit geven vu tsu arbetn.

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:52.717
yidn zaynen in Poyln geven dray a halbe milyon.

00:15:53.533 --> 00:15:58.100
yidn a sakh, un di polyakn hobn yidn nit spetsyel holt gehat,

00:15:58.100 --> 00:16:01.593
un zey hobn undz nit spetsyel gevolt tsulozn oyf arbet,

00:16:01.684 --> 00:16:05.200
iz yidn hobn gemuzt arbetn oyf di hantverkeray,

00:16:05.200 --> 00:16:06.630
oyf di kleyne arbet,

00:16:06.630 --> 00:16:08.900
un dos iz geven kleyne parnose.

00:16:09.649 --> 00:16:11.651
hob ikh nit gekont khasene hobn.

00:16:11.691 --> 00:16:12.697
⟨kh'hob⟩ nit kh-...

00:16:11.742 --> 00:16:15.350
ir hot nisht gehat genug parnose khasene tsu hobn?

00:16:14.627 --> 00:16:18.120
az me darf hobn a shtub un me darf hobn vu tsu lebn.

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:19.590
me darf firn a lebn.

00:16:19.251 --> 00:16:21.236
un ir hot gemuzt helfn...

00:16:19.590 --> 00:16:21.703
un der lebn ven es kumt a kind,

00:16:21.703 --> 00:16:24.240
 ikh hob dokh gezen vi andere...

00:16:22.980 --> 00:16:26.000
un ir hot gemuzt helfn di eltern nokh?

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:28.847
ir hot nokh gemuzt helfn e- ayere eltern?

00:16:27.469 --> 00:16:30.760
hel- hob ikh gemuzt helfn di eltern in shtub.

00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:32.590
kh'hob nit gekont avekgeyn fun shtub.

00:16:32.590 --> 00:16:34.747
un bay undz iz geven a balebatishkeyt,

00:16:34.747 --> 00:16:39.740
mit ⟨a, ki,⟩ s'iz geven a tsayt a ferd. dortn UNK geven azetike balebatishkeyt,

00:16:39.740 --> 00:16:43.340
vos lozt dos opet, iz, iz dos avekgegangen,

00:16:43.340 --> 00:16:45.450
un d- un dos khapn krik kon men nit.

00:16:45.450 --> 00:16:47.105
a mol voltn mir nemen

00:16:47.230 --> 00:16:50.650
fun dorf a mentshn, zol helfn. ikh gib aykh a ba-...

00:16:50.650 --> 00:16:53.501
oder ven ⟨a, i⟩metser volt gekont gebn

00:16:53.676 --> 00:16:56.254
gelt; m'hot gedarft firn.

00:16:55.540 --> 00:16:58.300
ven, ven ir zent geven UNK...

00:16:56.254 --> 00:16:59.160
un dem foter, dem foter... ikh vil aykh ⟨nor⟩ zogn...

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:02.782
dem foter hot nit spetsyel geart vegn dem.

00:17:03.261 --> 00:17:06.304
er volt avekgeyn in shul davnen, kumen shabes,

00:17:06.304 --> 00:17:09.980
makhn kide-..., ir veyst dokh oto di ale yidishe zakhn.

00:17:09.980 --> 00:17:13.590
firn, m'hot gemuzt haltn di shtub reyn, di kinder onton.

00:17:13.590 --> 00:17:15.640
es iz dokh nit geven a zakh!

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:20.247
iz azoy arum hob ikh, bin ikh geblibn, nit geven khasene gehat.

00:17:20.440 --> 00:17:25.360
un der, der foter iz geven a kh-, a khasidisher yid? s'iz geven,

00:17:24.570 --> 00:17:25.529
ver?

00:17:25.360 --> 00:17:28.100
s'iz geven a khasidishe shtub bay enk?

00:17:26.936 --> 00:17:28.922
a, bay undz a khasidishe.

00:17:28.530 --> 00:17:30.289
velkhe khasides?

00:17:28.940 --> 00:17:35.920
UNK mir zaynen, mir zaynen gehert, der foter, tsu Libavitsher khasidim, Libavitsher shul. bay undz iz geven azoy:

00:17:35.920 --> 00:17:37.810
geven khsidim, un s'iz geven

00:17:37.810 --> 00:17:41.930
misnagdim, oybe ir veyst... misnagdim iz itster enlekh

00:17:41.930 --> 00:17:45.570
⟨ot vi oto do a⟩ konservative shul. ikh gib aykh a bayshpil.

00:17:45.570 --> 00:17:47.570
der foter iz geven fun di khsidim.

00:17:47.570 --> 00:17:49.430
tsvey rabonim iz geven,

00:17:49.430 --> 00:17:53.620
vos di yidn voltn zikh sht- klaybndik aroyf shtendik krign

00:17:53.620 --> 00:17:55.490
un hargen zikh derfar;

00:17:55.490 --> 00:17:59.245
dos iz a khsidisher rov, dos iz a misnag⟨di⟩sher rov...

00:17:57.818 --> 00:18:01.610
s'iz geven makhloykes in enkere sht- i- in, in, in...?

00:17:59.623 --> 00:18:02.180
geven bay di eltern makhloykes,

00:18:02.180 --> 00:18:04.089
nor ikh'l aykh zogn: ikh,

00:18:04.348 --> 00:18:08.763
UNK nokh di militer hob ikh zikh nit gemisht in di ale makhloykesn.

00:18:07.926 --> 00:18:10.755
ir hot nisht gehat keyn teyl in dem?

00:18:09.428 --> 00:18:14.960
ikh hob nit gehat keyn tsayt un ikh hob zikh farnumen mit a, a⟨, in gantsn andere zakhn⟩.

00:18:14.040 --> 00:18:16.180
UND ir zent geven in a...

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:19.423
nu, mir voltn geyn farbrengen, mir voltn geyn, ikh'l aykh zogn, s'iz geven a klub,

00:18:19.423 --> 00:18:23.140
un geyn tantsn. s'iz dokh nit geven, mir zaynen dokh geven a mol,

00:18:21.730 --> 00:18:24.373
s'iz geven yidishe⟨, s'-⟩...

00:18:23.140 --> 00:18:25.520
mir zaynen dokh a mol geven yunge.

00:18:25.710 --> 00:18:28.878
s'iz geven yidishe ORGANISATIONEN?

00:18:27.484 --> 00:18:33.485
geven yidishe org- itster organizatsye yidishe. yidishe organizatsye iz geven bay undz aza:

00:18:33.610 --> 00:18:35.561
geven Shomer Hatsair,

00:18:36.647 --> 00:18:41.000
Tsienistn, Algemeyne Tsienistn, Poyle-Tsienistn,

00:18:41.153 --> 00:18:43.554
ot ot azetike zakh. ikh...

00:18:43.554 --> 00:18:46.311
un s'iz geven bay undz linke oykh.

00:18:46.367 --> 00:18:48.690
ir veyst vos s'heyst linke?

00:18:48.915 --> 00:18:50.579
geven linke.

00:18:50.822 --> 00:18:55.878
iz mentshn, yeder hot gehat ⟨zikh⟩ UNK zayne, zayne zakhn.

00:18:56.290 --> 00:18:58.123
a mol UNK der...

00:18:56.695 --> 00:19:02.291
ir zent geven a khaver in epes a partey tsi in epes a yidishe ORGANISATION?

00:18:59.985 --> 00:19:07.522
ikh bin, ikh bin a mol geven in Poyle-Tsienist, a Poyle-Tsienist bin ikh a mol... ikh bin gekumen aheym,

00:19:07.528 --> 00:19:13.440
hob ikh shoyn gehat a karte RZEMIEŚLNICZ⟨e⟩, oybe ir veyst... ir veyst dokh vos dos iz, a karte RZEMIEŚLNICZ⟨e⟩.

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:15.760
mir hobn zikh farnumen mit di arbeter.

00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:19.987
mir volt men shoyn veln klaybn aher, klaybn ahin. nu, ⟨kh'bin shoyn ge-⟩...

00:19:19.987 --> 00:19:23.370
a shtetl, a shtetl iz in aza zin:

00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:28.228
s'iz geven ⟨sht-⟩ vos mentshn hobn opgelebt un zey hobn dem ban in di oygn nit gezen.

00:19:28.960 --> 00:19:32.160
ir farshteyt mir? zey hobn keyn ban nit gezen,

00:19:32.160 --> 00:19:34.387
zaynen in der velt ergets nit geven.

00:19:35.220 --> 00:19:39.000
un ikh bin shoyn geven a mentsh, ikh bin in Varshe, in Varshe, a mol iz dokh,

00:19:39.000 --> 00:19:41.370
in Varshe geven, dos iz geven

00:19:41.370 --> 00:19:44.309
a groyse zakh in yen- in yenem yorhundert.

00:19:45.075 --> 00:19:49.280
oto dos iz shoyn bald, bald mit a akhtsik yor tsurik.

00:19:49.260 --> 00:19:50.180
yo.

00:19:50.728 --> 00:19:51.897
ir farshteyt?

00:19:51.897 --> 00:19:55.703
iz, iz ikh, volt men shoyn mir klaybn do un klaybn dortn,

00:19:55.703 --> 00:19:59.660
nor in, eyn mol hot men mir gevolt klaybn in shtot-rat,

00:19:59.660 --> 00:20:02.605
in, in der yidish- in der poylisher.

00:20:02.605 --> 00:20:04.950
mir hot men nit durkhgelozt.

00:20:05.292 --> 00:20:09.660
mir hot men nit durkhgelozt; zey hobn gehaltn az ikh bin a linker mentsh, ⟨iz, ⟩...

00:20:09.660 --> 00:20:11.490
ikh hob nit gepast far zey,

00:20:11.490 --> 00:20:13.500
vayle ikh hob shtendik geven,

00:20:13.500 --> 00:20:17.650
mayn lebn un di khaveyrim un alts, ikh'l aykh zogn, tsvishn arbeter.

00:20:18.117 --> 00:20:21.770
ikh bin gegangen mit a veg in gantsn an andere;

00:20:21.770 --> 00:20:25.650
ikh hob nit gekrokhn ergets, ikh hob gegangen tsevishn di arbeter.

00:20:25.650 --> 00:20:29.810
⟨zikh ts⟩⟨UNK⟩, a mol voltn mir leyenen rusishe bikher, geven Gorki,

00:20:29.810 --> 00:20:31.890
di linke bikher vayzn,

00:20:31.890 --> 00:20:34.465
volt zikh undz oysdukhtn az Rusland

00:20:34.465 --> 00:20:36.842
iz beser. ir farshteyt?

00:20:35.953 --> 00:20:39.070
ir hot zikh gedakht az Rusland iz beser.

00:20:38.020 --> 00:20:43.260
 ikh hob a mol oykh getrakht az Rusland iz, iz, az s'iz do vos tsu arbetn...

00:20:43.260 --> 00:20:45.274
mentshn on arbet,

00:20:45.274 --> 00:20:49.296
yugntlekhe umgeyn fray un frank,

00:20:49.420 --> 00:20:53.960
kukn... a mol hob ikh gearbet dortn in a shul, hob ikh gehat tsu makhn ongenumen...

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:56.766
ikh fleg geyn oyf di TARGes fun di melukhishe.

00:20:56.766 --> 00:21:01.080
iz oyf TARGes volt geyn der vos volt gelt aynleygn. ikh hob gehat a ⟨b-⟩

00:21:01.080 --> 00:21:04.230
kh'hob ⟨al-⟩ zayendik a y- nokh a, a yunger mentsh,

00:21:04.230 --> 00:21:08.640
hob ikh gehat a P.K.O. bikhl, volt ikh im aynleygn dem P.K.O. bikhl un ikh volt geyn,

00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:11.130
un TARGes volt ikh nemen. far vos?

00:21:11.130 --> 00:21:15.090
kh'volt zikh bakonen mitn sekretar, gebn im etlekhe zlot, ⟨⟩...

00:21:15.090 --> 00:21:17.240
es iz dokh, do azetike zakhn...

00:21:17.240 --> 00:21:20.466
volt er mir makhn, "shrayb azoy fil." dos iz dos.

00:21:20.466 --> 00:21:25.950
⟨volt ikh⟩ UNK. hob ikh gearbet, voltn ale khevre kumen zitsn, kukn vi ikh arbet.

00:21:25.950 --> 00:21:29.975
ir farshteyt? s'iz nit geven keyn groyser lebn in Dokshits

00:21:29.975 --> 00:21:32.010
kegn, far di yugntlekhe,

00:21:32.010 --> 00:21:37.406
afile ⟨Shomer Hatsair⟩. yederer iz gezesn oyf di tate-mame's pleytse.

00:21:37.665 --> 00:21:40.983
zaynendik afile iber tsvantsik yor,

00:21:40.990 --> 00:21:43.840
iz men gezesn oyf di tate-mame's pleytse.

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.585
m'hot gelebt tsuzamen...

00:21:43.940 --> 00:21:45.170
un ir...

00:21:45.585 --> 00:21:48.190
s'iz nit geven azoy... haynt

00:21:48.190 --> 00:21:50.990
shtelt zikh mir, ot ikh in mayn elter,

00:21:50.990 --> 00:21:52.999
shtelt zikh mir for a lebn.

00:21:53.055 --> 00:21:55.749
vi azoy hot men gekont a mol lebn?

00:21:56.802 --> 00:21:58.940
az m'hot gehat zeks kinder,

00:21:58.940 --> 00:22:01.841
mit eyn shtub, vos iz geshtanen fun dray tsimern,

00:22:03.096 --> 00:22:05.570
di kikh, bakn broyt aleyn,

00:22:05.678 --> 00:22:07.191
vashn di vesh...

00:22:07.264 --> 00:22:09.598
ir veyst vi? ot ot azoy.

00:22:09.598 --> 00:22:14.320
hodeven zeks kinder, gebn alemen a hemd onton. me darf dokh, m'darf dokh lebn.

00:22:14.320 --> 00:22:17.433
un a froy aleyn! di froy hot gearb-...

00:22:17.727 --> 00:22:20.690
vi di froy hot gearbet iz a mol,

00:22:20.690 --> 00:22:23.678
iz haynt iz dos, kon men dos nit bashraybn.

00:22:24.021 --> 00:22:25.685
me kon dos nit bashraybn!

00:22:27.430 --> 00:22:31.423
dos, oto dos iz geven in ale kleynshtetlekh...

00:22:31.851 --> 00:22:36.688
in di bikher leyent men dokh... ale kleynshtetlekh di zelbe zakh!

00:22:36.711 --> 00:22:39.804
ver es hot gekont, dem tsholnt volt araynshteln

00:22:39.804 --> 00:22:41.970
oyf bay nakht, farmakhn dem oyvn,

00:22:41.970 --> 00:22:46.427
UNK aroysnemen oyf morgn dem esn. ir farshteyt? dos iz nit geven...

00:22:46.427 --> 00:22:50.002
KHASHMAL iz bay undz ersht gevorn in finf un draysiktn yor.

00:22:50.397 --> 00:22:54.576
mir hobn geve⟨UNK⟩t oyf a lomp mit, ne- mit neft,

00:22:54.582 --> 00:22:57.056
aroyfdreyen a lomp mit neft.

00:22:57.872 --> 00:23:01.860
heytsn mit holts, tseklapn oyf shtiklekh, darfn unterheytsn di oyvn...

00:23:01.860 --> 00:23:04.370
s'iz nit geven alts vi ⟨its-⟩ vi azoy.

00:23:04.370 --> 00:23:06.754
m'hot gedarft hobn an ort oyf haltn holts,

00:23:06.754 --> 00:23:08.565
an ort oyf haltn hey.

00:23:08.959 --> 00:23:12.500
kormen di beheymes, darf men kokhn tep un ⟨zey⟩ gebn.

00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:17.030
un dem top, ir, oybe ir veyst, s'iz geven aza vilke vos me volt araynrukn,

00:23:17.030 --> 00:23:20.270
aroysshlepn dem top, ⟨hot men⟩ gedarft hobn ⟨koyekh⟩.

00:23:20.333 --> 00:23:23.010
dos iz di, dos iz geven di froy.

00:23:24.467 --> 00:23:28.308
ir hot gefilt ANTISEMITISMUS in ayer shtot?

00:23:28.315 --> 00:23:32.440
vegn dem veln mir nokh oykh kumen, az mir veln kumen... UNK...

00:23:30.335 --> 00:23:33.660
ikh red yetst farn krig, als kind.

00:23:32.440 --> 00:23:38.320
a- ales kind? ikh'l aykh zogn: al- ikh hob zikh gehodevet tsevishn kristn, ikh.

00:23:33.761 --> 00:23:35.910
als bokher, als kind.

00:23:38.320 --> 00:23:42.478
far vos? vayle mir hobn gelebt, iz geven antkegn undz a dokter,

00:23:42.478 --> 00:23:46.930
un dortn iz geven eyner an ag- eyner iz geven a, an agronom,

00:23:46.930 --> 00:23:49.430
der tsveyter iz geven a polyak, a rus.

00:23:49.430 --> 00:23:53.919
mir zaynen geven a gemisht, dortn iz dokh geven Vay- dos iz geven Vaysrusland,

00:23:53.919 --> 00:23:56.299
nor polyakn hobn oykh gelebt dortn.

00:23:56.299 --> 00:24:00.945
⟨zey hobn tsvishn zikh...⟩ keyn gr- ikh hob ⟨in⟩ kind zayendik keyn antisemitizm nit gefilt.

00:24:00.410 --> 00:24:01.870
nisht gefilt.

00:24:01.137 --> 00:24:06.851
ven hob ikh gefilt dem antisemitizm? az m'iz greser gevorn, m'iz gekumen in Vilne,

00:24:06.857 --> 00:24:10.180
un dortn hobn mir shoyn gefilt dem antisemitizm.

00:24:09.355 --> 00:24:14.242
in di kley- in shtetl nisht, bloyz in, bloyz in d- in Vilne?

00:24:10.620 --> 00:24:12.940
in di shtetlekh, in Dokshits,

00:24:12.940 --> 00:24:17.769
in Dokshits iz nit geven keyn, keyn... ikh'l aykh zogn, ikh hob dos nit gefilt,

00:24:18.079 --> 00:24:22.700
vayl ikh, ikh bin geven gehodevet, ikh bin geven gehodevet,

00:24:22.700 --> 00:24:28.580
ale hobn mir gerufn, "LEYB⟨A⟩, IDI SYUDA!" ⟨der, a-⟩ az ikh bin geven a khaver tsevishn,

00:24:28.580 --> 00:24:29.860
tsevishn zey.

00:24:28.710 --> 00:24:31.353
tsvishn nisht yidishe kinder oykh.

00:24:29.860 --> 00:24:33.490
tsevishn di kristlekhe ki- kinder ⟨bin ikh oykh⟩ geven a khaver.

00:24:33.490 --> 00:24:36.050
kh'volt geyn bay nakht fun kheyder,

00:24:36.050 --> 00:24:39.910
a lanterne... veyst ir vi me balaykht? di shtot iz dokh geven fintster.

00:24:39.910 --> 00:24:43.318
me nemt a butl, me shtelt arayn a likhtl, un me geyt...

00:24:43.847 --> 00:24:48.270
un ikh bin gegangen fun kheyder vayt, zeyer vayt, un gegangen,

00:24:48.270 --> 00:24:50.210
un far keynem nit moyre gehat.

00:24:49.517 --> 00:24:51.240
nisht moyre gehat.

00:24:50.374 --> 00:24:54.750
neyn. ikh bin ni- ikh bin geborn gevorn un ikh hob nit moyre gehat.

00:24:54.750 --> 00:24:57.614
ikh bin geven fun andere, fun andere kind-...

00:24:57.614 --> 00:25:02.297
kh'hob a mol ts- a mol hob ikh zikh geshlogn, ⟨ot⟩ a mol hot der foter gehat fun mir a bisl...

00:25:02.297 --> 00:25:05.370
ikh hob tseharget a pritsishn zun.

00:25:05.683 --> 00:25:09.150
a pri- er iz geven a porets, aza min sort, a groyser

00:25:09.150 --> 00:25:14.008
mentsh, hot er gelebt nit vayt fun undz, mir hobn zikh geshpilt, un er hot zikh ⟨mit mir⟩ UNK un ikh hob im gegebn.

00:25:14.008 --> 00:25:19.396
er iz avek aheym veynendik, un gekumen de⟨m⟩ foter. ikh hob zikh bahaltn, iz gekumen de⟨m⟩ foter.

00:25:19.858 --> 00:25:25.002
⟨zogt er, nu⟩... oto dos treft azetike zakhn. ikh'l aykh zogn, mir konen nit reydn,

00:25:25.002 --> 00:25:29.800
ikh gedenk dokh nit al dem yugnt, nor oto dos iz geven der yugnt.

00:25:30.017 --> 00:25:32.240
s'iz geven alerley zaytn,

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:36.020
nor ikh, spetsyel, in di yunge yorn, zayendik a kind,

00:25:36.020 --> 00:25:38.420
hob ikh far di poyerim nit moyre gehat.

00:25:38.607 --> 00:25:41.244
neyn. ikh bin geven a frayer mentsh.

00:25:41.244 --> 00:25:44.956
UNK nu, nakher iz geven shoyn bay mir der tsveyter bruder,

00:25:41.440 --> 00:25:42.670
in di yorn...

00:25:44.956 --> 00:25:47.420
hobn mir shoyn gehat a KOAKH.

00:25:47.584 --> 00:25:53.610
⟨geven a mol, hot men⟩ zikh mit zey tseharg- oder s'iz nit geven azoy, a- azoy.

00:25:53.610 --> 00:25:58.090
der tsveyter bruder mayner iz geven a shtarkerer fun mir, oykh a breyter, a gezunter.

00:25:58.090 --> 00:26:02.360
a, ikh hob zayn bild, vet men dos darfn opfotografirn. ikh hob zaynem a bild.

00:26:02.586 --> 00:26:04.300
er... UNK...

00:26:02.603 --> 00:26:05.258
kh'volt aykh gevolt fregn, in di yo- di

00:26:05.258 --> 00:26:07.470
ende yorn draysik,

00:26:07.470 --> 00:26:14.072
ir hot, m'hot gevust in Dokshits vos s'tut zikh in DEUTSCHLAND? m'hot gefilt, se geyt kumen a krig?

00:26:11.918 --> 00:26:15.034
o, i- n- i- ot ikh vel aykh dertseyln:

00:26:15.343 --> 00:26:18.340
kumendik tsu nayn un draysiktn yor,

00:26:18.448 --> 00:26:22.002
ven s'iz shoyn tsu undz gekumen di Sovyetn,

00:26:22.363 --> 00:26:23.555
di Sovyetn...

00:26:22.532 --> 00:26:25.980
ven zenen gekumen di Sovyetn keyn Dokshits?

00:26:25.215 --> 00:26:26.069
vos?

00:26:25.980 --> 00:26:28.270
ven iz dos geven? velkhe...

00:26:26.970 --> 00:26:31.841
in nayn, in nayn un draysik, umgefer in, in september.

00:26:31.802 --> 00:26:34.760
in september zenen shoyn geven di Sovyetn?

00:26:33.653 --> 00:26:35.388
di Sovyetn bay undz.

00:26:35.388 --> 00:26:39.823
arayngeforn mit tankes, un ikh bin geshtanen oyfn hoyf un gekukt.

00:26:39.863 --> 00:26:41.820
ikh bin aroys fun shtub,

00:26:41.820 --> 00:26:44.590
un mir zaynen geven di ts-... hob ikh aykh gevizn...

00:26:44.590 --> 00:26:49.141
di tsveyte shtub funem arayngang fun Rusland, oyfn grenets.

00:26:49.141 --> 00:26:50.860
un zey zaynen glaykh arayn,

00:26:50.860 --> 00:26:55.220
un UNK... "ZDRAVSTVUY!" hot er oyfgehoybn di hant un gezogt mir, "ZDRAVSTVUY!"

00:26:55.220 --> 00:26:57.830
afile a polyak mit a biks iz aroysgelofn,

00:26:57.830 --> 00:27:00.869
UNK dos iz geven tsum lakhn.

00:27:00.869 --> 00:27:04.717
UNK azetike tankes forn arayn, ⟨⟩, mit a biks!

00:27:04.717 --> 00:27:08.173
nu, ikh hob, zikh geg- gegrist un avekgegangen.

00:27:08.550 --> 00:27:11.330
ikh'l aykh zogn, dos iz geven...

00:27:08.905 --> 00:27:11.920
di kristn zenen antlofn demolts?

00:27:11.330 --> 00:27:12.220
vos?

00:27:11.920 --> 00:27:15.345
di kristn zenen antlofn ven di rusn zenen arayn?

00:27:13.393 --> 00:27:18.888
neyn! k- keyn, antlofn zaynen di vos zaynen, di politseyske.

00:27:19.536 --> 00:27:22.230
politseyske zaynen ale tselofn.

00:27:22.422 --> 00:27:26.530
di, keyn militer hobn mir shoyn nit gezen. mir veysn afile nit ⟨vu zaynen⟩...

00:27:26.530 --> 00:27:31.101
ikh'l aykh zogn az s'iz geven azoy, azoy, umge-

00:27:31.101 --> 00:27:34.370
az s'iz, mir hobn nit gevust vi azoy iz dos,

00:27:34.370 --> 00:27:36.742
un mir hobn nit gezen keyn poylishe armey.

00:27:36.790 --> 00:27:39.010
ir hot nisht gevust az,...

00:27:38.335 --> 00:27:43.920
mir hobn gevust az, ⟨, di p-⟩ az Daytshland hot farnumen a teyl Poyln,

00:27:42.958 --> 00:27:43.863
Poyln.

00:27:43.920 --> 00:27:47.170
un, dos hobn mir yo gevust, vayl s'iz dokh geven in radyo,

00:27:47.170 --> 00:27:51.770
un P- un P- un Rusland, un Rusland geyt farnemen a teyl Poyln.

00:27:47.481 --> 00:27:49.348
ir hot gehat a radyo?

00:27:51.105 --> 00:27:54.241
ets hots gehat a radyo, tsaytungen?

00:27:53.100 --> 00:27:55.480
a rad- mir hobn gehat a radyo.

00:27:55.480 --> 00:27:59.439
a mol hob ikh, hobn mir geleyent a ⟨ts⟩aytung, geven di,

00:27:59.715 --> 00:28:02.510
 "Moment."

00:28:02.449 --> 00:28:04.890
di yid- a yidishe tsaytung?

00:28:02.510 --> 00:28:04.430
"Moment" iz geven. ye.

00:28:04.430 --> 00:28:05.330
un s'-... a vos?

00:28:05.330 --> 00:28:08.910
a yidishe. yidishe tsaytungen zaynen tsu undz gegangen in shtetl

00:28:05.360 --> 00:28:07.083
a yidishe tsaytung?

00:28:08.910 --> 00:28:12.115
di gantse, di gantse tsayt far Poyln. der "Haynt,"

00:28:12.115 --> 00:28:14.970
der "Haynt" iz geven a Tsienistishe tsaytung,

00:28:15.021 --> 00:28:19.970
un der "Moment" iz geven a, an ander tsay- oykh a yidishe, beyde yidishe.

00:28:19.970 --> 00:28:21.579
dos volt geyn in shtetl...

00:28:20.792 --> 00:28:23.756
m'hot geredt bay enk yidish in shtub?

00:28:22.176 --> 00:28:27.360
yidish. in gantsn, in shtub hot men geredt yidish afile ven di rusn zaynen gekumen,

00:28:27.360 --> 00:28:29.100
⟨ven⟩ mir zaynen in land gekumen.

00:28:29.100 --> 00:28:31.285
mayne kinder konen yidish,

00:28:31.285 --> 00:28:34.129
vayle di, di eltern hobn mir dokh gebrakht,

00:28:34.129 --> 00:28:37.040
iz hobn zey gehodevet di kinder.

00:28:37.040 --> 00:28:39.146
mayne kinder konen yidish.

00:28:39.405 --> 00:28:43.140
di eyniklekh shoyn nit, nor di kinder konen yidish.

00:28:44.097 --> 00:28:53.820
nu, dos iz geven. itster vel ikh aykh d- dertseyln, oto dos iz geven a yugnt. me hot farbrakht, m'hot getantst: der in hore getantst, un der hot d⟨o⟩ getantst.

00:28:44.350 --> 00:28:45.350
⟨i-...⟩

00:28:53.820 --> 00:28:56.730
s'iz nit geven eyn, eyn GAL yidn.

00:28:57.107 --> 00:29:00.570
⟨s'iz⟩ dokh geven alerleyike: s'iz geven yidn velkhe hobn farbrakht,

00:29:00.570 --> 00:29:04.950
s'iz geven yidn fun raykhn, geven krayz raykhere,

00:29:04.950 --> 00:29:08.812
vos hobn zikh gehaltn, nor keyn spetsyele klubn hobn zey oykh nit gehat.

00:29:09.055 --> 00:29:13.900
bay undz iz nit geven keyn, s'iz di shtetl kleyn geven, geven a por toyznt yidn, UNK...

00:29:13.932 --> 00:29:17.166
undz vel'mir vayter geyn oyf di nekste kasete.

00:29:13.965 --> 00:29:15.330
⟨s'iz nit g-⟩...

00:29:17.172 --> 00:29:18.990
BESEDER? undz vel'mir...

00:29:17.847 --> 00:29:20.288
yo. ⟨i-⟩ nu, itster shoyn geendikt?

00:29:19.740 --> 00:29:23.740
yo., m'vet endikn, di nekste kasete vet men vayter geyn.

00:29:20.530 --> 00:29:23.830
UNK
